segments.text: Welcome back! I'm ready to help you log
your last meeting while it's fresh. To
kick things off, who was the client or
company you met with today?
I just met with Adidas.
Adidas!
Perfect. Got that locked in. Now, was this
a new customer meeting, or were you doing
a periodical business review with them?
Yeah, it was a periodical business review
meeting.
Got it. So we're looking at a periodical
business review with Adidas. Let me dig
into how things are actually going on the
current contract. How are things looking
overall? Any space protection issues on
the vessels you've been using with them?
Nothing special overall. They are happy
with the service so far. We are at about
five hundred TEUs per month, and that's
the idea for the next six months.
That is huge! Five hundred TEUs per month
is solid
volume, and I love that you're locked in
for the next six months.
Okay, so things are running smooth on the
service side. No space protection
headaches. Now, are you seeing any
specific seasonality or volume trends with
Adidas lately? Anything shifting in their
patterns?
No, it's stable for the near future.
Fair enough.
So it's pretty steady across the board
with them. Let me ask you this: What's
their forecast looking like beyond those
next six months? Are they thinking about
ramping up, staying flat, or is it too
early to say?
It's too early to say. We have another
meeting in two weeks, and then we will
know more, and I will call you again to
summarize it, and then we will move on.
Perfect. Two weeks out, you'll have more
intel. I'll be ready for that debrief
call. Before we wrap up, though, did you
manage to touch on any commercial
excellence topics with them, like our
digital tools or anything that could add
value down the line?
Yeah, yeah, yeah, we did that last week.
They know everything.
Excellent!
So you've already covered the commercial
excellence angle. All right, end of the
day, did you actually achieve the
objectives you went in with for today's
meeting?
Yeah.
Perfect. I've polished the summary and
sent it off. Drive safe!
